1 mage is needed, to tank the leftover while people med to finish, bards are not very good tanks against tough MOBs, earth pet is great for this.<br>
<br>
Druids are kind of useless in these groups, the AE spell delay is too huge.  The spot is better taken by a fast AE caster or another chanter to help with stuns or to gflux.<br>
<br>
