For Flame Arc ALONE:<br>
dmg/second = 25.8<br>
dmg/mana = .91 (per target)<br>
mana/second = 28.4<br>
500 mana buys: 455 dmg in 17.6 seconds<br>
<br>
For Scintilation ALONE:<br>
dmg/second = 93.3<br>
dmg/mana = 1.68 (per target)<br>
mana/second = 55.5<br>
500 mana buys: 840 dmg in 9.1 seconds<br>
<br>
For Flame Arc + Scintillation:<br>
dmg/second = 94.9<br>
dmg/mana = 1.41 (per target)<br>
mana/second = 67.5<br>
500 mana buys: 705 dmg in 7.4 seconds<br>
<br>
Just for a frame of reference... chances are you'd be better off sticking char/shock in that last slot for finishing off the last 1 or 2 mobs than putting Flame Arc there, but that's just my opinion... <p><table width="100%" border="0">
