<br>
I think most all classes would actually be very limited in their abilities to pump out the kind of dmg and efficiency an AE group demands.  I say efficiency because the lower level you are, the less mana efficient your spells are.  The higher level the enc, the longer he can keep stunning, mezzing, etc.  Same goes with any class... even clerics I'd think.  Take a low level enc and ask him to chain cast stun, he's gonna run oom pretty quick probably.  Add in the fact all the dmg dealers are taking longer with their less efficient spells, and I don't think the outcome would be very good. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :/ --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/ohwell.gif ALT=":/"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   To make it even worse, the low level cleric would have a much harder time keeping everyone healed.  That part, I can say is a fact. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><center><img src=http://facelink.com/edit/raw/rawimage/82/1800182.jpg></center>
